üìù DESCRIPTION
------------------------------
This n8n workflow automates a 3-step email sequence for lead generation, complete with follow-ups and reply detection. It uses a Google Sheet to manage your contacts and track the status of each email.

What it does

Automated Email Sequencing:** Sends a series of three emails to a list of contacts from a Google Sheet.
Reply Detection:** Checks for replies to your emails and stops the sequence for that contact if a reply is received.
Status Tracking:** Updates the Google Sheet to show which emails have been sent and whether a contact has replied.
Slack Notifications:** Sends notifications to a Slack channel to keep you updated on the workflow's progress.
Scheduling:** The workflow is triggered on a schedule, which you can customize.
Timezone and Multi-account Support:** Includes nodes to handle sending emails from multiple accounts and in different timezones.

Who it's for

Sales Teams:** To automate lead nurturing and follow-up with prospects.
Marketers:** To run automated email campaigns and track engagement.
Business Owners:** To save time on outreach and ensure consistent communication with potential customers.

How to set it up

Google Sheet:
    Create a copy of the Google Sheets template.
    In the "Google Sheets" nodes, select your Google Sheets account and enter the copied spreadsheet's ID.

Gmail:
    In the "Gmail" nodes, select your Gmail account.
    Customize the email subject and body in each "Gmail" node.

Slack:
    In the "Slack" nodes, select your Slack account and the channel where you want to receive notifications.

Scheduling:
    Adjust the "Schedule Trigger" nodes to set the timing for your email sequences.

Activate the workflow:
    Once you have configured the nodes, activate the workflow to start the automation.
